channel.title: In desperate need of help with understanding jar files!
channel.description:
Ok i noticed on alot of servers there are these jar files but older ones like delta-scape dont have them (I think thats what there called) Here is a pic! [img]http://img126.imageshack.us/img126/306/jardv7.png[/img] could some one help me understand how to make jar files and how to get them to work with your server for example the file i took a pic of, titled Autospawn.cfg i think everyone knows what it dose
So i need help understanding these files. I would like to add a few to my server.
